These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 10

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, iced-tea, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, dancing, rock-climbing, fishing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, country, classical, salsa
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 2. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan salsa##3
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the fan country##6
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person drinking iced-tea or the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the fan classical, but not both##10
 6. the person drinking iced-tea and the fan dubstep have the same parity positions##9
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan classical##3
 8. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the fan salsa##5
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person drinking cola and the fan dubstep##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | iced-tea   | water      | cola    |
| Hobby         | writing     | rock-climbing | dancing | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | classical       | dubstep | salsa         | country     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-2::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, nectarine, eggplant, cabbage
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, russian, brazilian, colombian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, lizard, goat
 1. the turkish is the person eating cabbage or the owner of the goat is the turkish, but not both##10
 2. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 3. the turkish is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
 4. the owner of the lizard and the turkish have different parity positions##9
 5. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 8. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
 9. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
11. the colombian is in an even position##4
12. the turkish is the person eating watermelon or the turkish is the owner of the goat, but not both##10
13. the person eating watermelon is not to the right of the person eating eggplant##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | cabbage | nectarine    | watermelon | eggplant    |
| Nationality   | brazilian   | turkish | russian  | colombian |
| Pet           | lizard     | goat    | chinchilla    | ferret    |

