1. the person eating blueberry is the egyptian##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
3. the person eating blueberry is the brazilian or the person eating blueberry is the person drinking water, but not both##10
4. the person eating broccoli is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
5. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
6. the mexican is between the person eating cranberry and the egyptian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk         | mirinda     | water | juice |
| Food          | cranberry | radish | blueberry         | broccoli   |
| Nationality   | chinese     | mexican   | egyptian       | brazilian   |

