.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-4::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, potato, peas, onion
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, magic-tricks, skydiving, gardening
There are 4 different nationalities: german, spanish, pakistani, nigerian
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the spanish##1
 2. the german is not to the right of the person eating peas##8
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the german##6
 6. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is the pakistani or the person who's hobby is gardening is the person eating potato, but not both##10
 8. the pakistani is the person eating peas or the pakistani is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks, but not both##10
 9. the nigerian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person eating peas##7
10. the nigerian is on the right of the person eating peach##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | onion  | peach   | potato | peas  |
| Hobby         | drawing     | skydiving  | magic-tricks | gardening |
| Nationality   | german | spanish | nigerian  | pakistani |

