.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, coffee, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, romance, zombie, satire
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goldfish, turtle
 1. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person watching romance movies##6
 3. the owner of the fish is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching sports movies##2
 4. the person drinking water is not the person watching satire movies##6
 5. the owner of the turtle and the person watching sports movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person drinking sprite is the person watching sports movies or the person drinking sprite is the owner of the chinchilla, but not both##10
 7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
 8. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
10. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
11. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking tea##7
12. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | sprite   | tea | water | coffee   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | romance    | sports   | satire |
| Pet           | chinchilla    | fish | goldfish    | turtle  |

