 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
 4. the person driving the tram and the colombian have different parity positions##9
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the colombian is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
 7. the pakistani is on the far right##1
 8. the italian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the thai##7
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the colombian is between the person driving the airplane and the italian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | writing   | drawing | woodworking  | dancing |
