 6. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 8. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
 9. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##8
10. the person watching family movies is the person who's hobby is sudoku or the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person eating blueberry, but not both##10
