.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-20::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, pomegranate, garlic, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, spy, horror, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, rat, snake
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 2. the owner of the hamster is the person watching horror movies or the owner of the hamster is the person eating avocado, but not both##10
 3. the person eating garlic is not to the right of the person watching spy movies##8
 4. the person eating garlic is not to the left of the owner of the hamster##8
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
 6. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4
 7. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 8. the person eating pomegranate is the owner of the rat##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
10. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person watching time-travel movies##6
11. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
12. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
13. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | pomegranate   | avocado | zucchini  | garlic        |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | time-travel      | horror    | spy |
| Pet           | rat   | snake    | hamster | chinchilla      |

 